data.description: ***OPEN HOUSE, SATURDAY, MARCH 2ND 12-3PM AND SUNDAY, MARCH 3RD 12-3PM*** Welcome to the exciting Redbird Ranch, a resort style neighborhood unlike any other that you can call home.  Situated on a corner lot, this beautiful 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath home with multiple living spaces awaits your every need.  Working from home is no longer an issue with a separate spacious office.  With 2 eating areas and a bright spacious kitchen with gas cooking, this is becomes an entertainers dream.  Gatherings outside are an entertainers dream, choose from the enclosed patio or the spacious outdoor patio.  The time has come to make this beautiful home yours.  Kitchen refrigerator and washer/dryer to convey. **Roof and water heater 2022.  Back Patio 2023.  Back and front yard recently seeded.
